    ,(295, 'Sidney’s annual spring time snowman is standing tall.', 'Sidney’s annual spring time snowman is standing tall.  You would never guess that just yesterday (4/16/2015) our painters finished painting our house..yes the outside.   This picture was snapped by our neighbor.', 'Sidney’s annual spring time snowman is standing tall.  You would never guess that just yesterday (4/16/2015) our painters finished painting our house..yes the outside.   This picture was snapped by our neighbor.'+CHAR(13)+CHAR(10)+''+CHAR(13)+CHAR(10)+'![934997659867566.jpg](/api/post-image/934997659867566.jpg)', '2015-04-17 17:36:00', NULL, 1, 1, 0, '2015-04-17 17:36:00', 'B189EB60-B5B5-458B-B54C-B18CC35619DD', '2026-07-10 23:16:00', 'B189EB60-B5B5-458B-B54C-B18CC35619DD', '/Image/PostImages/934997659867566.jpg', NULL, 1)
    ,(296, 'Sidney''s first away from the backyard camping trip was quite a hit at11 mile reservoir.', 'Sidney''s first away from the backyard camping trip was quite a hit at11 mile reservoir.  She liked peeling the corn more than eating it.  She also loved setting up the tent and sleeping in it almost as much as she likes her princess tent(thanks aunt Shannon).', 'Sidney''s first away from the backyard camping trip was quite a hit at11 mile reservoir.  She liked peeling the corn more than eating it.  She also loved setting up the tent and sleeping in it almost as much as she likes her princess tent(thanks aunt Shannon).'+CHAR(13)+CHAR(10)+''+CHAR(13)+CHAR(10)+'![983364995030832.jpg](/api/post-image/983364995030832.jpg)', '2015-07-12 23:21:00', NULL, 1, 1, 0, '2015-07-12 23:21:00', 'B189EB60-B5B5-458B-B54C-B18CC35619DD', '2026-07-10 23:16:00', 'B189EB60-B5B5-458B-B54C-B18CC35619DD', '/Image/PostImages/983364995030832.jpg', NULL, 1)
    ,(297, 'Today is the anniversary of the passing of Axel Roerig.', 'Today is the anniversary of the passing of Axel Roerig.  He was without a doubt, one of the best people I have ever had the pleasure of knowing.'+CHAR(13)+CHAR(10)+''+CHAR(13)+CHAR(10)+'Most people knew him as an adventurous rock climber that lived as close to a nomad as anyone over his last couple years.  I remember him as the guy that would go ice climbing, even though he hated cold fingers.  He would help me figure out the backwards wiring in my house, even if it meant we nearly burnt the place down.  He was more than willing to he', 'Today is the anniversary of the passing of Axel Roerig.  He was without a doubt, one of the best people I have ever had the pleasure of knowing.'+CHAR(13)+CHAR(10)+''+CHAR(13)+CHAR(10)+'Most people knew him as an adventurous rock climber that lived as close to a nomad as anyone over his last couple years.  I remember him as the guy that would go ice climbing, even though he hated cold fingers.  He would help me figure out the backwards wiring in my house, even if it meant we nearly burnt the place down.  He was more than willing to help me move a heavy refrigerator, hang drywall, or lend a hand while I was landscaping.  More than anything, he was a great friend and he is missed. '+CHAR(13)+CHAR(10)+''+CHAR(13)+CHAR(10)+'Thanks to the folks that keep his memories around.  I found a couple links, but if anyone else has any, please pass them along.'+CHAR(13)+CHAR(10)+''+CHAR(13)+CHAR(10)+'http://www.rockclimbing.com/photos/Trad/Axel_Roerig_on_4X4_67962.html'+CHAR(13)+CHAR(10)+''+CHAR(13)+CHAR(10)+'http://archives.wcexaminer.com/index.php/2006/08/16/thomas-roerig/'+CHAR(13)+CHAR(10)+''+CHAR(13)+CHAR(10)+'https://ablack.wordpress.com/2006/08/12/trajic-passing-of-thomas-axel-roerig/'+CHAR(13)+CHAR(10)+''+CHAR(13)+CHAR(10)+'![999439450090053.jpg](/api/post-image/999439450090053.jpg)'+CHAR(13)+CHAR(10)+''+CHAR(13)+CHAR(10)+'![999442013423130.jpg](/api/post-image/999442013423130.jpg)', '2015-08-07 18:48:00', NULL, 1, 1, 0, '2015-08-07 18:48:00', 'B189EB60-B5B5-458B-B54C-B18CC35619DD', '2026-07-10 23:15:00', 'B189EB60-B5B5-458B-B54C-B18CC35619DD', '/Image/PostImages/999439450090053.jpg', NULL, 1)
