    ,(381, 'Please copy and paste this to your status if you''re constantly being asked to copy and paste things to your status by people who copy and paste things to their statuses. Many people won''t copy and paste this, but my truly sarcastic friends (who are my...', 'Please copy and paste this to your status if you''re constantly being asked to copy and paste things to your status by people who copy and paste things to their statuses. Many people won''t copy and paste this, but my truly sarcastic friends (who are my favorites) will copy and paste it because they''re sarcastic by nature. If you don''t copy and paste it, then this means you hate bacon. And if you hate bacon, the government wins, and a unicorn dies. Possibly puppies as well. And occasionally baby g', 'Please copy and paste this to your status if you''re constantly being asked to copy and paste things to your status by people who copy and paste things to their statuses. Many people won''t copy and paste this, but my truly sarcastic friends (who are my favorites) will copy and paste it because they''re sarcastic by nature. If you don''t copy and paste it, then this means you hate bacon. And if you hate bacon, the government wins, and a unicorn dies. Possibly puppies as well. And occasionally baby goats. But never dragons because of something to do with tomatoes.', '2020-07-31 00:48:00', NULL, 1, 0, 0, '2020-07-31 00:48:00', 'B189EB60-B5B5-458B-B54C-B18CC35619DD', '2026-07-10 19:33:00', 'B189EB60-B5B5-458B-B54C-B18CC35619DD', '', 1, 1)
