    ,(388, 'French lessons on Duolingo', 'We were walking around the Evergreen lake in the first week of the new year discussing what we would like to do this year.  Sidney, who has been hitting the French lessons on Duolingo for 300+ days said she wanted to go to eat a baguette in France and visit the Eiffel Tower.  Whelp, apparently Jeri and I are easily influenced and highly vacation starved.  Paris - what a wonderful trip and a ton of great experiences for the whole family.', 'We were walking around the Evergreen lake in the first week of the new year discussing what we would like to do this year.  Sidney, who has been hitting the French lessons on Duolingo for 300+ days said she wanted to go to eat a baguette in France and visit the Eiffel Tower.  Whelp, apparently Jeri and I are easily influenced and highly vacation starved.  Paris - what a wonderful trip and a ton of great experiences for the whole family.'+CHAR(13)+CHAR(10)+''+CHAR(13)+CHAR(10)+'![We were walking around the Eve.jpg](/api/post-image/We were walking around the Eve.jpg)'+CHAR(13)+CHAR(10)+''+CHAR(13)+CHAR(10)+'![We were walking around the Eve.jpg](/api/post-image/We were walking around the Eve(1).jpg)', '2022-03-24 23:21:00', NULL, 1, 1, 0, '2022-03-24 23:21:00', 'B189EB60-B5B5-458B-B54C-B18CC35619DD', '2026-07-10 19:02:00', 'B189EB60-B5B5-458B-B54C-B18CC35619DD', '/Image/PostImages/We were walking around the Eve(1).jpg', NULL, 1)
