    ,(400, 'Greece - 2025 \ 2026', 'We headed to Greece to celebrate the holidays and ring in the new year.', 'Super fun trip to check out Greece - It did not dissappoint.  '+CHAR(13)+CHAR(10)+''+CHAR(13)+CHAR(10)+'![Greece - 2025  2026.png|600](/api/post-image/Greece%20-%202025%20%202026.png)'+CHAR(13)+CHAR(10)+''+CHAR(13)+CHAR(10)+'Took a few wrong attempts to get to the top of Mount Lycabettus - near St. George chapel, but we got there.'+CHAR(13)+CHAR(10)+'![Greece - 2025  2026.png|600](/api/post-image/Greece%20-%202025%20%202026%281%29.png)'+CHAR(13)+CHAR(10)+''+CHAR(13)+CHAR(10)+'If you didn''t know, Sidney really likes cats, and Athens is loaded with cats.'+CHAR(13)+CHAR(10)+'![Greece - 2025  2026.png|600](/api/post-image/Greece%20-%202025%20%202026%282%29.png)'+CHAR(13)+CHAR(10)+''+CHAR(13)+CHAR(10)+'NMR scaling the cliff behind Apollo''s temple in Delphi.'+CHAR(13)+CHAR(10)+'![Greece - 2025  2026.png|600](/api/post-image/Greece%20-%202025%20%202026%283%29.png)'+CHAR(13)+CHAR(10)+''+CHAR(13)+CHAR(10)+'Looks like a great place to catch a show. Our guide said Cold Play and U2 have both played there recently.'+CHAR(13)+CHAR(10)+'![Greece - 2025  2026.png|600](/api/post-image/Greece%20-%202025%20%202026%284%29.png)'+CHAR(13)+CHAR(10)+''+CHAR(13)+CHAR(10)+'A picture of the Caryatids - which is a fancy way of saying sculpted female figures serving as columns on the Erechtheion temple. Yes - that is Erechtheion - not the autocorrected version (Ere**ion)'+CHAR(13)+CHAR(10)+'![Greece - 2025  2026.png|600](/api/post-image/Greece%20-%202025%20%202026%285%29.png)'+CHAR(13)+CHAR(10)+''+CHAR(13)+CHAR(10)+'Chef Spero put Jeri on the stir pot later. And might I say, she is the bechamel queen.'+CHAR(13)+CHAR(10)+'![Greece - 2025  2026.png|600](/api/post-image/Greece%20-%202025%20%202026%286%29.png)'+CHAR(13)+CHAR(10)+''+CHAR(13)+CHAR(10)+'Sidney and Chef Spero at The Artist boutique hotel in Monastiraki/Psirri.'+CHAR(13)+CHAR(10)+'![Greece - 2025  2026.png|600](/api/post-image/Greece%20-%202025%20%202026%287%29.png)'+CHAR(13)+CHAR(10)+''+CHAR(13)+CHAR(10)+'That is a fully flowing chocolate wall behind us - and we are partaking in Gelato with fancy dipped & flavored cones.'+CHAR(13)+CHAR(10)+'![Greece - 2025  2026.png|600](/api/post-image/Greece%20-%202025%20%202026%288%29.png)', '2026-01-06 00:00:00', NULL, 1, 1, 0, '2026-01-06 00:00:00', 'B189EB60-B5B5-458B-B54C-B18CC35619DD', '2026-07-11 20:54:00', 'B189EB60-B5B5-458B-B54C-B18CC35619DD', '/Image/PostImages/Greece - 2025 %202026.png', NULL, NULL)


